pop3-server - developer guide

1) Running the tests
2) Release NPM Module


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Running the tests

Currently there is a set of mocha (https://github.com/visionmedia/mocha)
based unit and integration tests.

To run the tests within node.js type:
$ npm test


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Release NPM Module

Adjust the module version in package.json. The execute the following:

$ git commit -a
$ npm install
$ npm test
$ npm publish
$ git tag <released version>
$ git push
$ git push --tags
